  {
    "id": "f_csv_80e186ed0e",
    "slug": "you-know-the-sad-thing-of-post-9-11-which-was-of-course-horrific-was-that-the",
    "texto": "You know, the sad thing of post-9/11, which was of course horrific, was that the city in which I felt completely at home for two decades, suddenly people like us - brown people - were looked at as the 'Others.'",
